<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="protect-v">protect <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prə'tekt/    美 /prə'tekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 保护；防护：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>protect the earth
保护地球</p></div>

<ul>
<li>protect sb / sth from sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We put a sheet of plastic across the floor to protect us from the damp.
我们在地板上铺了一块塑料膜以防潮。</p><footer>2009 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Something must be done to protect the environment from being polluted.
必须采取措施以保护环境免受污染。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>protect (sb / sth) against sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Physical exercise can protect you against heart disease.
体育锻炼可以预防心脏病。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Waxing your car will help protect against rust.
给车打蜡可以防止生锈。</p></div>

<h3 id="defend-guard-protect">辨析 defend, guard, protect</h3>
<ol>
<li>三者都含有“保护”之意。<br />
<strong>defend</strong> 指 “保卫” 、 “防御” ， 指抵御或击退外来的攻击。此外，defend 还有“辩护”之意。
<strong>guard</strong> 指“守护” 、 “看守” ， 指保持警惕或注意来防止危险发生。
<strong>protect</strong>  语义范围广 ， 指 “保护” ， 以免遭受危险、 伤害等。</li>
</ol>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We're doing whatever we can to <strong>protect</strong> our environment <strong>from</strong> pollution.
我们正在尽最大努力来保护环境免受污染。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>protective /prə'tektɪv/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s very <strong>protective of</strong> his younger brother.
他很爱护他的弟弟。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>He was wearing dark glasses to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (保护) his eyes from the sun.  （2006 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. protect  </p></div>